Our notecards (including white envelopes) are 4 1/4" X 5 1/2", printed on matte white heavyweight cards.  The notecards are blank inside so that you can share your thoughts, sentiments, and greetings with your friends, family, and co-workers for any occasion.  Enjoy and come away with us!

5X7 and 8X10 enlargements are printed on glossy photo paper.
